OL,3,CIranian man conflicted by war says he
OL,4,Cfears for safety of family
OL,6,FAsylum seeker Aslan says he worries
OL,7,Ffor friends and family as bombs
OL,8,Fcontinue to drop while he feels
OL,9,Fconflicted by the war in Iran
OL,11,FAn Iranian man living on North
OL,12,FTyneside says he fears for the safety
OL,13,Fof his parents in Tehran while
OL,14,Ftensions in the Middle East continue
OL,15,Fto escalate.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
