FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1772733968
OL,3,CIranian man conflicted by war says he
OL,4,Cfears for safety of family
OL,6,FAslan told ITV News Tyne Tees he felt
OL,7,Fconflicted by what the US and Israeli
OL,8,Fstrikes on Iran would mean for the
OL,9,Ffuture of his country - but if bombs
OL,10,Fcontinued there remained a chance of
OL,11,Fhis loved ones being at risk.
OL,13,F"It's a nightmare," he said. "It's
OL,14,Fjust a nightmare, with hope."
OL,16,FAslan's family still live in Tehran
OL,17,Fwhere many American and Israeli
OL,18,Fattacks have hit. But the chance the
OL,19,Fwar could hasten the end of a
OL,20,Fmurderous regime means he welcomes the
OL,21,Fbombs.
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1772733968
OL,3,CIranian man conflicted by war says he
OL,4,Cfears for safety of family
OL,6,F"Their bombing is very accurate and
OL,7,Ftheir target is just government, not
OL,8,Fthe people, but war is war," he said.
OL,9,F"You never know that bombs might be
OL,10,Fmistake (sic) or something - that is
OL,11,Fobvious.
OL,13,F"We are so worried about our family
OL,14,Fand friends in Iran. But we kind of
OL,15,Fgive it trust because we need it in
OL,16,Fthese circumstanced."
OL,26,@rD@IpmrD@Mpn
