OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1772733968
OL,3,CIranian man conflicted by war says he
OL,4,Cfears for safety of family
OL,6,FIran has launched a wave of
OL,7,Fretaliatory attacks across the Middle
OL,8,FEast after US-Israeli strikes killed
OL,9,FSupreme Leader Ayatollah Ali Khamenei
OL,10,Fjust one day after conflict began.
OL,12,FAt least 787 people have been killed
OL,13,Fin Iran according to the Iranian Red
OL,14,FCrescent Society.
OL,16,FBefore he left Iran seven years ago,
OL,17,FAslan was the drummer and singer in a
OL,18,Frock band.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
