OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1772733968
OL,3,CIranian man conflicted by war says he
OL,4,Cfears for safety of family
OL,6,FLeaving with his wife and son in the
OL,7,Fface of religious persecution, he is
OL,8,Fnow seeking asylum in the UK and is
OL,9,Fone of 2,000 Iranians living in the
OL,10,Fregion.
OL,12,FHe said he knew this war would happen
OL,13,Fand he remains hopeful that his family
OL,14,Fcould soon live in a free Iran.
OL,16,F"No one wants their country to be
OL,17,Fattacked but millions of Iranian
OL,18,Fpeople - we were happy," he added.
OL,19,F"It's really a strange feeling, you
OL,20,Fknow. Because in this situation we
OL,21,Freally need foreign help."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
