OL,3,CIranian man conflicted by war says he
OL,4,Cfears for safety of family
OL,6,FA volunteer for charity Walking With,
OL,7,FAslan has struggled to keep in contact
OL,8,Fwith his family due to intermittent
OL,9,Finternet access since a regime change
OL,10,Flast year.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FAnd while there are many like Aslan
OL,18,Fwho have come here from Iran and still
OL,19,Fhave family there, there are a
OL,20,Fsignificant number of UK citizens
OL,21,Fliving in the Middle East.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
