OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1772733968
OL,3,CIranian man conflicted by war says he
OL,4,Cfears for safety of family
OL,6,FThe government today said it estimates
OL,7,F300,000 Brits are living in the region
OL,8,Fwhile 130,000 of those have registered
OL,9,Fwith the Foreign Office to receive
OL,10,Fupdates and advice.
OL,12,FSome of those will be British
OL,13,Fresidents and others swill be
OL,14,Fholidaymakers.
OL,16,FThe first flights took off from the
OL,17,Fregion last night and though flights
OL,18,Fto Newcastle have not yet resumed,
OL,19,Ftravellers from the North East have
OL,20,Flanded at both Heathrow and Manchester
OL,21,FAirports.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
