OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1772733968
OL,3,CIranian man conflicted by war says he
OL,4,Cfears for safety of family
OL,6,FSome holidaymakers from the North East
OL,7,Fwho arrived back on UK soil described
OL,8,Ftheir experience in the Middle East as
OL,9,F"petrifying"
OL,11,FAmong them were Abbie and Kevin Yorke,
OL,12,Ffrom Bishop Auckland, who flew with
OL,13,Ftheir son Beau from Dubai to Heathrow
OL,14,FAirport after having their original
OL,15,Fflight to Newcastle cancelled.
OL,17,FThey told ITV News they had been
OL,18,Fsleeping in the basement of their
OL,19,Fhotel in Dubai.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
