PN,42609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1772733968
OL,3,CIranian man conflicted by war says he
OL,4,Cfears for safety of family
OL,6,FAbbie described their experience as
OL,7,F"petrifying".
OL,9,FAnother traveller, from Middlesbrough,
OL,10,Farrived in Manchester on Tuesday but
OL,11,Fsaid his father had been stranded
OL,12,Fabroad.
OL,14,FHe said the flight he returned on was
OL,15,Fonly half full and the airspace was
OL,16,Fclosed after they lifted off.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/9
